{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775860429873,"sessionID":"ses_286793199ffe2oTho7Qcp6DGO8","part":{"id":"prt_d79872b8a001fye6ybkVDhXAE3","messageID":"msg_d798718e7001uyh5Y4XrE1bbc0","sessionID":"ses_286793199ffe2oTho7Qcp6DGO8","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_b7c113d13ec648a0a2a5322f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 Tasks\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Implementation Ready)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Project Setup\n\n- [ ] **T001** Create `pyproject.toml` with project metadata and dependencies (typer, pydantic, pyyaml, rich, docker, httpx)\n- [ ] **T002** Create `agentcube/__init__.py` with `__version__` and exports\n- [ ] **T003** Create `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` CLI subpackage marker\n- [ ] **T004** Create `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` with runtime exports\n- [ ] **T005** Create `agentcube/services/__init__.py` services package marker\n- [ ] **T006** Create `agentcube/models/__init__.py` models package marker\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Data Models\n\n- [ ] **T010** Implement `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model in `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` with all fields (agent_name, language, entrypoint, port, build_mode, description, requirements_file, etc.)\n- [ ] **T011** Add `validate_language` Pydantic validator (python/java only)\n- [ ] **T012** Add `validate_build_mode` Pydantic validator (local/cloud only)\n- [ ] **T013** Add `validate_port` Pydantic validator (1-65535 range)\n- [ ] **T014** Implement `MetadataOptions` dataclass in `agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: MetadataService\n\n- [ ] **T020** Implement `MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)` with fallback chain (agent_metadata.yaml → agent.yaml → metadata.yaml)\n- [ ] **T021** Implement `MetadataService.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)` with YAML dump\n- [ ] **T022** Implement `MetadataService.validate_workspace(workspace_path)` basic validation\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: DockerService\n\n- [ ] **T030** Implement `DockerService.generate_python_dockerfile(metadata)` returning Dockerfile content string\n- [ ] **T031** Implement `DockerService.generate_java_dockerfile(metadata)` returning Dockerfile content string\n- [ ] **T032** Implement `DockerService.write_dockerfile(workspace_path, content)` to write Dockerfile file\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: PackRuntime\n\n- [ ] **T040** Implement `PackRuntime.__init__(verbose)` initializing services\n- [ ] **T041** Implement `PackRuntime._validate_workspace_structure(workspace_path)` - raises ValueError if missing\n- [ ] **T042** Implement `PackRuntime._load_or_create_metadata(workspace_path, options)` with fallback chain and defaults\n- [ ] **T043** Implement `PackRuntime._apply_option_overrides(metadata, options)` CLI option merging\n- [ ] **T044** Implement `PackRuntime._validate_language_compatibility(workspace_path, metadata)` language validation\n- [ ] **T045** Implement `PackRuntime._validate_python_compatibility(workspace_path)` - checks for *.py files\n- [ ] **T046** Implement `PackRuntime._validate_java_compatibility(workspace_path)` - checks for pom.xml\n- [ ] **T047** Implement `PackRuntime._process_dependencies(workspace_path, metadata)` dispatcher\n- [ ] **T048** Implement `PackRuntime._process_python_dependencies(workspace_path)` - validates requirements.txt (optional)\n- [ ] **T049** Implement `PackRuntime._process_java_dependencies(workspace_path)` - validates pom.xml exists\n- [ ] **T050** Implement `PackRuntime._generate_dockerfile(workspace_path, metadata)` - skips if exists\n- [ ] **T051** Implement `PackRuntime._prepare_output_path(workspace_path, output_path)` - creates directory if needed\n- [ ] **T052** Implement `PackRuntime._update_pack_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, dockerfile_path)` - saves YAML\n- [ ] **T053** Implement `PackRuntime._infer_entrypoint(workspace_path, language)` - finds main.py or main class\n- [ ] **T054** Implement main `PackRuntime.pack(workspace_path, **options)` orchestrating all steps\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: CLI Interface\n\n- [ ] **T060** Create `agentcube/cli/main.py` with Typer app definition\n- [ ] **T061** Implement `pack` command with all options (-f/--workspace, --agent-name, --language, --entrypoint, --port, --build-mode, --description, --output, --verbose)\n- [ ] **T062** Implement `version_callback` for --version option\n- [ ] **T063** Implement `_handle_error(e, command_name, verbose)` with Rich error formatting\n- [ ] **T064** Add Rich `console` and success `Progress` spinner output\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: CLI Entry Point\n\n- [ ] **T070** Configure `[project.scripts]` in pyproject.toml for `kubectl-agentcube` entry point\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T080** Write test for `PackRuntime._validate_workspace_structure` - missing directory raises ValueError\n- [ ] **T081** Write test for `PackRuntime._validate_workspace_structure` - valid Python workspace passes\n- [ ] **T082** Write test for `PackRuntime._validate_workspace_structure` - valid Java workspace passes\n- [ ] **T083** Write test for `PackRuntime._validate_python_compatibility` - no Python files raises ValueError\n- [ ] **T084** Write test for `PackRuntime._validate_java_compatibility` - no pom.xml raises ValueError\n- [ ] **T085** Write test for `PackRuntime._load_or_create_metadata` - loads existing metadata file\n- [ ] **T086** Write test for `PackRuntime._load_or_create_metadata` - creates defaults when no file\n- [ ] **T087** Write test for `PackRuntime._apply_option_overrides` - CLI options override metadata\n- [ ] **T088** Write test for `AgentMetadata` validators - invalid language raises ValidationError\n- [ ] **T089** Write test for `AgentMetadata` validators - invalid port raises ValidationError\n- [ ] **T090** Write test for `PackRuntime._infer_entrypoint` - finds main.py for Python\n- [ ] **T091** Write test for `PackRuntime._generate_dockerfile` - skips when Dockerfile exists\n- [ ] **T092** Write test for `PackRuntime.pack` end-to-end with valid workspace\n\n---\n\n## Phase 9: Integration Tests\n\n- [ ] **T100** Write integration test for `pack` command with Python workspace\n- [ ] **T101** Write integration test for `pack` command with Java workspace\n- [ ] **T102** Write integration test for `pack --output` custom path\n- [ ] **T103** Write integration test for `pack --verbose` error output\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- typer[all] >= 0.9.0\n- pydantic >= 2.0.0\n- pyyaml >= 6.0\n- rich >= 13.0.0\n- docker >= 6.0.0\n- httpx >= 0.24.0\n- packaging >= 23.0\n- importlib-resources >= 6.0.0\n- semver >= 3.0.0\n\n**Dev Dependencies:**\n- pytest >= 7.0.0\n- pytest-asyncio\n- pytest-cov\n- pytest-mock\n- ruff\n- mypy\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Install package\npip install -e .\n\n# Run pack command\nkubectl-agentcube pack --help\nkubectl-agentcube pack -f /path/to/workspace\n\n# Run tests\npytest tests/ -v\nruff check agentcube/\nmypy agentcube/\n```\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Design stage ST-3 completed - ready for implementation\n- All tasks are independently verifiable (each task has clear pass/fail criteria)\n- T001-T006 (Phase 1) must be completed before any runtime code\n- T010-T014 (Phase 2) required before T020-T022 (MetadataService)\n- T020-T022 required before T040-T054 (PackRuntime)\n- T030-T032 required before T050 (Dockerfile generation)\n- CLI tests in T080-T092 can run in parallel after runtime is complete","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775860429855,"end":1775860429870}}}}
